Package: shinyDesign2
Type: Package
Title: Tools for sequencing-based spatial transcriptomics experimental design
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Juan", "Xie", , "juanxie.84@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for simulating sequencing based spatial transcriptomics data to 	facilitate experimental designs. 
    Includes integration with Seurat, Shiny modules for interactive analysis, and utility functions for performance evaluation.
